==== Qualifications ====
The proofreader role is assigned if the user holds the "Proofreader" role on VRChat’s [[Special:MyLanguage/Discord servers#VRChat Localization|Localization community]] for [https://docs.vrchat.com/docs/suggesting-localization-changes Crowdin]. New proofreaders may also be chosen after consistently publishing quality edits for their known language(s).